title: 'The Movies': Everything to watch after the '90s episode
paragraphs: In the mood for a ’90s movie marathon?

You could start with this list of films featured in CNN’s Original Series “The Movies.” Each week, the show will focus on a different decade as filmmakers, actors and critics share the stories behind your favorite films.
Below you’ll find all of the movies discussed in the ’90s episode – and if you missed it, you can catch up here on CNNgo.
